window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Outgunned and outnumbered after the world fell into chaos, Sergeant Jason Walker and his military service dog, MMax, desperately need the women around them to become warfighters. The ladies have the determination and grit to meet the challenges of the apocalypse, but can they kill the brutal thugs attacking their community? Sergeant Maria McGill helps Jason prepare their inexperienced but willing females to fight with unusual tactics and weapons.</p> <p>Jason and Maria survived the war in England, a plane crash, and the end of the world as we knew it, but can they train the women in their community fast enough to fight off a determined and well-armed foe? These Amazon warriors fight and die to save their friends and loved ones in this post-apocalyptic survival story.</p>"; 
